{"id":22,"date":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","date_gmt":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/?page_id=22"},"modified":"2023-04-13T08:31:59","modified_gmt":"2023-04-13T00:31:59","slug":"admission-requirements","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/admission-requirements\/","title":{"rendered":"Admission"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Applicants must submit or accomplish the following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-3\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><tbody><tr><td>1. Admission Form (OU Form1)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>2. One (1) recommendation letter from your former professors\/supervisor (OU Form2)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>3. Permit to study from head of your agency if employed (OU Form 3)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>4. Official Transcript of Records and Transcript of Records (Transfer Credential)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>5. Two (2) photocopy of PSA birth certificate and marriage certificate (for married)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>6. Payment of Application Fee of \u20b1100 for Local and $25 for foreign nationals (Non-refundable).<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>7. An essay of about 300 words indicating your purpose for applying to the distance education program and your plan after completing the degree.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>8. \u00a0Latest identical ID picture (2\u201d x 2\u201d) with plain white background.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>9. Valid visa for foreign nationals. (Foreign student only)<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 1 Admission Form<\/a> <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 2 Recommendation Form<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 3 Permit to Study<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Applicants must take note of the following deadlines of submission.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>QUARTER<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>DEADLINE<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>First Semester S.Y 2023-2024<\/td><td>2nd week of July<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Second Semester S.Y 2022-2023<\/td><td>2nd week of October<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>MID YEAR<\/td><td>2nd week of April<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><\/td><td><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-5\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/index.php\/contact-us\/\">Contact Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Applicants must submit or accomplish the following: 1. Admission Form (OU Form1) 2. One (1) recommendation letter from your former professors\/supervisor (OU Form2) 3. Permit to study from head of your agency if employed (OU Form 3) 4. Official Transcript of Records and Transcript of Records (Transfer Credential) 5. Two (2) photocopy of PSA birth certificate and marriage certificate (for married) 6. Payment of Application Fee of \u20b1100 for Local and $25 for foreign nationals [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_price":"","_stock":"","_tribe_ticket_header":"","_tribe_default_ticket_provider":"","_tribe_ticket_capacity":"0","_ticket_start_date":"","_ticket_end_date":"","_tribe_ticket_show_description":"","_tribe_ticket_show_not_going":false,"_tribe_ticket_use_global_stock":"","_tribe_ticket_global_stock_level":"","_global_stock_mode":"","_global_stock_cap":"","_tribe_rsvp_for_event":"","_tribe_ticket_going_count":"","_tribe_ticket_not_going_count":"","_tribe_tickets_list":[],"_tribe_ticket_has_attendee_info_fields":false},"ticketed":false,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/22"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=22"}],"version-history":[{"count":35,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/22\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1073,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/22\/revisions\/1073"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/w